title: Watergate Survivor: An Interview with Dr. David Young '59
itunes:title: Watergate Survivor: Interview with Dr. David Young '59
description: Dr. David Young '59, Special Assistant to Henry Kissinger and founder of Oxford Analytica shares about his time in the White House with a focus on the qualities needed, lessons learned and the spiritual dimension of political power.
